{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "dra:numbers.33",
    "translationId": "dra",
    "bookSlug": "numbers",
    "chapterNumber": 33,
    "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33",
    "summary": "Source text for Numbers 33 in Douay-Rheims Bible (Challoner)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.1",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:1",
      "text": "These are the mansions of the children of Israel, who went out of Egypt by their troops under the conduct of Moses and Aaron,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.2",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:2",
      "text": "Which Moses wrote down according to the places of their encamping, which they changed by the commandment of the Lord.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.3",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:3",
      "text": "Now the children of Israel departed from Ramesses the first month, on the fifteenth day of the first month, the day after the phase, with a mighty hand, in the sight of all the Egyptians,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.4",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:4",
      "text": "Who were burying their firstborn, whom the Lord had slain (upon their gods also he had executed vengeance,)",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.5",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:5",
      "text": "And they camped in Soccoth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.6",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:6",
      "text": "And from Soccoth they came into Etham, which is in the uttermost borders of the wilderness.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.7",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:7",
      "text": "Departing from thence they came over against Phihahiroth, which looketh towards Beelsephon, and they camped before Magdalum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.8",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:8",
      "text": "And departing from Phihahiroth, they passed through the midst of the sea into the wilderness: and having marched three days through the desert of Etham, they camped in Mara.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.9",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:9",
      "text": "And departing from Mara, they came into Elim, where there were twelve fountains of waters, and seventy palm trees: and there they camped.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.10",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:10",
      "text": "But departing from thence also, they pitched their tents by the Red Sea. And departing from the Red Sea,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.11",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:11",
      "text": "They camped in the desert of Sin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.12",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:12",
      "text": "And they removed from thence, and came to Daphca.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.13",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:13",
      "text": "And departing from Daphca, they camped in Alus.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.14",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:14",
      "text": "And departing from Alus, they pitched their tents in Raphidim, where the people wanted water to drink.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.15",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:15",
      "text": "And departing from Raphidim, they camped in the desert of Sinai.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.16",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:16",
      "text": "But departing also from the desert of Sinai, they came to the graves of lust.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.17",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:17",
      "text": "And departing from the graves of lust, they camped in Haseroth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.18",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:18",
      "text": "And from Haseroth they came to Rethma.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.19",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:19",
      "text": "And departing from Rethma, they camped in Remmomphares.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.20",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:20",
      "text": "And they departed from thence and came to Lebna.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.21",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:21",
      "text": "Removing from Lebna they camped in Ressa.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.22",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:22",
      "text": "And departing from Ressa, they came to Ceelatha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.23",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:23",
      "text": "And they removed from thence and camped in the mountain Sepher.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.24",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:24",
      "text": "Departing from the mountain Sepher, they came to Arada,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.25",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:25",
      "text": "From thence they went and camped in Maceloth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.26",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:26",
      "text": "And departing from Maceloth, they came to Thahath.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.27",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:27",
      "text": "Removing from Thahath they camped in Thare.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.28",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:28",
      "text": "And they departed from thence, and pitched their tents in Methca.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.29",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:29",
      "text": "And removing from Methca, they camped in Hesmona.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.30",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:30",
      "text": "And departing from Hesmona, they came to Moseroth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.31",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:31",
      "text": "And removing from Moseroth, they camped in Benejaacan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.32",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:32",
      "text": "And departing from Benejaacan, they came to mount Gadgad.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.33",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:33",
      "text": "From thence they went and camped in Jetebatha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.34",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:34",
      "text": "And from Jetebatha they came to Hebrona.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.35",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:35",
      "text": "And departing from Hebrona, they camped in Asiongaber.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.36",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:36",
      "text": "They removed from thence and came into the desert of Sin, which is Cades.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.37",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:37",
      "text": "And departing from Cades, they camped in mount Hor, in the uttermost borders of the land of Edom.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.38",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:38",
      "text": "And Aaron the priest went up into mount Hor at the commandment of the Lord: and there he died in the fortieth year of the coming forth of the children of Israel out of Egypt, the fifth month, the first day of the month,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.39",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:39",
      "text": "When he was a hundred and twenty-three years old.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.40",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:40",
      "text": "And king Arad the Chanaanite, who dwelt towards the south, heard that the children of Israel were come to the land of Chanaan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.41",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:41",
      "text": "And they departed from mount Hor, and camped in Salmona.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.42",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:42",
      "text": "From whence they removed and came to Phunon.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.43",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:43",
      "text": "And departing from Phunon, they camped in Oboth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.44",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:44",
      "text": "And from Oboth they came to Ijeabarim, which is in the borders of the Moabites.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.45",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:45",
      "text": "And departing from Ijeabarim they pitched their tents in Dibongab.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.46",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:46",
      "text": "From thence they went and camped in Helmondeblathaim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.47",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:47",
      "text": "And departing from Helmondeblathaim, they came to the mountains of Abarim over against Nabo.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.48",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:48",
      "text": "And departing from the mountains of Abarim, they passed to the plains of Moab, by the Jordan, over against Jericho.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.49",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:49",
      "text": "And there they camped from Bethsimoth even to Ablesatim in the plains of the Moabites,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.50",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:50",
      "text": "Where the Lord said to Moses:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.51",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:51",
      "text": "Command the children of Israel, and say to them: When you shall have passed over the Jordan, entering into the land of Chanaan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.52",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:52",
      "text": "Destroy all the inhabitants of that land: Beat down their pillars, and break in pieces their statues, and waste all their high places,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.53",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:53",
      "text": "Cleansing the land, and dwelling in it. For I have given it you for a possession.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.54",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:54",
      "text": "And you shall divide it among you by lot. To the more you shall give a larger part, and to the fewer a lesser. To every one as the lot shall fall, so shall the inheritance be given. The possession shall be divided by the tribes and the families.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.55",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:55",
      "text": "But if you will not kill the inhabitants of the land: they that remain, shall be unto you as nails in your eyes, and spears in your sides, and they shall be your adversaries in the land of your habitation.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:numbers.33.56",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:56",
      "text": "And whatsoever I had thought to do to them, I will do to you.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
